            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>截至台北時間15日10:10，櫃買市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>上漲6.25點（或3%），暫報214.86點。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li>近 1 週：-2.69%</li><li>近 1 月：-16.54%</li><li>近 3 月：-15.03%</li><li>近 6 月：-22.81%</li><li>今年以來：-18.46%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>焦點個股</em></p></section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>LED車燈概念領漲+6.75%。其中    堤維西(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1522:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1522\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1522-TW</a>)            上漲        9.95%            ;        麗清(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3346:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3346\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3346-TW</a>)            上漲        9.86%            ;        大億(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1521:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1521\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1521-TW</a>)            上漲        9.81%    。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>SDN概念領漲+5.03%。其中    華星光(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:4979:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/4979\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">4979-TW</a>)            上漲        9.77%            ;        眾達-KY(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:4977:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\